- Now, is that okay?
- Yes, Your Honor.

01:27:25.788 --> 01:27:27.589
That would be okay.

01:27:27.591 --> 01:27:29.691
<i>So, you can
take from A to give to B</i>

01:27:29.693 --> 01:27:31.026
<i>if B pays more taxes?</i>

01:27:31.028 --> 01:27:34.399
If it is a significant
amount, yes.

01:27:38.502 --> 01:27:40.969
<i>Mr. Bullock, you
have time remaining.</i>

01:27:40.971 --> 01:27:43.904
<i>Would you like to use it
for a rebuttal?</i>

01:27:43.906 --> 01:27:45.674
<i>Thank you, your Honor.</i>

