The one thing that all
poor neighborhoods share

01:27:55.017 --> 01:27:57.786
is that they don't produce
much tax revenue.

01:27:57.788 --> 01:28:00.792
<i>If the Court affirms
the lower court's decision,</i>

01:28:01.958 --> 01:28:05.093
then you would put
poor neighborhoods

01:28:05.095 --> 01:28:06.728
and working-class neighborhoods

01:28:06.730 --> 01:28:09.464
like Fort Trumbull
in jeopardy.

01:28:56.879 --> 01:28:58.813
Congratulations, Jim.

01:28:58.815 --> 01:29:00.581
We won.
Five to four.

