for someone to come in
and take your house,

01:29:08.091 --> 01:29:10.892
take your private property
against your will.

01:29:10.894 --> 01:29:12.594
The U.S. Supreme Court today

01:29:12.596 --> 01:29:14.696
affirmed the power
of local governments

01:29:14.698 --> 01:29:16.230
to seize private property.

01:29:16.232 --> 01:29:18.200
The government's right
to seize your home

01:29:18.202 --> 01:29:20.835
just received
a broad stamp of approval

01:29:20.837 --> 01:29:23.170
from the Supreme Court
of the United States.

01:29:23.172 --> 01:29:25.974
Man, it just seems
outrageous to me

01:29:25.976 --> 01:29:27.809
that you can take
private property

